captions.text:
Janine just liked one of
my photos on Instagram.
I've never even talked to Janine.
Like why would she like one of my photos?
She doesn't seem like a person

that will like just
any photo on Instagram.
How could I have been so blind.

If that's your quirky way
of asking me out, yes.
I will go out with you.
to profess your love to me on Instagram.
No ones ever made me feel the way
you make me feel right now.
I don't have a care in the world.
What color should my wedding tux be?
Did you just like Zack's photo?

He was gonna be the
best man at our wedding.

- Oh, Janine just liked
my photo on Instagram.
